Package ohos.data.orm

Class AllChangeToTarget

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.orm.AllChangeToTarget

  • public class AllChangeToTarget
extends Object
    An auxiliary class of data storage that stores all the added, deleted, and updated objects.

    If you have registered a data observer for the ORM database, all the added, deleted, and updated objects will be stored in the data storage so that the observer can obtain these objects.

    Since:
    1
    See Also:
    OrmObjectObserver
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_APPDATAMGR
